hero.about-Me: I provide training and mentoring to students in the early years of IT. I have a good skill set in different programming languages ​​and I am always keen to learn new things and explore more efficient working methods. I take online courses, attend specialized institutes, and share tutorials on my YouTube channel for beginners. I have 1250+ followers on Telegram, most of whom are students. Currently, I am focusing on web development and have made great progress in front-end development. My skills include using vue.js, react.js, and Next.js.
